text: Anne Martin (born September 24, 1961) is an American rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
